                            Services
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/patients">Gestion des Patients</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/appointments">Rendez-vous</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="/medical-records">Dossiers Médicaux</a></li>
